title: Marie Gluesenkamp Perez, a Democrat, Beats Joe Kent in Washington House Race
description: Marie Gluesenkamp Perez, an auto shop owner, defeated the Republican Joe Kent, a former Green Beret and combat veteran who denied the legitimacy of the 2020 election and backed Jan. 6 defendants.
dc:creator: Annie Karni

media:content.media:credit: Amanda Lucier for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Marie Gluesenkamp Perez emphasized abortion rights in her campaign.
